This repository documents the **Blueprint Pattern** itself (not an application under documentation).

## Identity

- **Project:** Blueprint Pattern — architecture documentation as a Markdown link graph for AI agents
- **Stack:** Markdown, Mermaid, GitHub Actions (link checker)

