| Resource | Path |
|----------|------|
| System prompt | [PROMPT.md](../../PROMPT.md) |
| Extensions | [docs/blueprint-pattern-extensions.md](../../docs/blueprint-pattern-extensions.md) |
| Templates | [docs/templates/architecture/](../../docs/templates/architecture/) |
| Sample app Blueprint | [docs/examples/sample-app/order-service/docs/architecture/blueprint.md](../../docs/examples/sample-app/order-service/docs/architecture/blueprint.md) |

## Session protocol

1. For pattern changes: read PROMPT.md and extensions guide.
2. For sample app work: read the sample `blueprint.md` and `context/always-on.md`.
3. Traverse via Markdown links; verify referential integrity on new links.

Application repos should replace this file with their own `docs/architecture/context/always-on.md` content.
